svt_axi_write_same_slave_sequence Class Reference

Inheritance diagram for class svt_axi_write_same_slave_sequence:

List of all members.

Detailed Description

This sequence generates a Write transactions with overlapping addr/non overlapping addr/random addr to the same slave. Remaining fields are randomized.
